Class MsgDelRange

  • java.lang.Object
    • co.tinode.tinodesdk.model.MsgDelRange

  • public class MsgDelRange
extends java.lang.Object
    MsgDelRange is either an individual ID (hi=0 || hi==null) or a range of deleted IDs, low end inclusive (closed), high-end exclusive (open): [low .. hi), e.g. 1..5 → 1, 2, 3, 4
